<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <title>Main Dashboard</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #000;
      --fg: #0f0;
      --accent: #ff0;
      --panel: #0a0a0a;
      --border: #0f0;
    }

    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    body {
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--fg);
      font: 13px 'Courier New', monospace;
      padding: 20px;
      min-height: 100vh;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    h1 {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 24px;
      letter-spacing: 4px;
      color: var(--fg);
      text-shadow: 0 0 10px var(--fg);
      margin-bottom: 40px;
      padding: 20px;
      border: 2px solid var(--border);
      background: var(--panel);
    }

    .nav-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
      gap: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }

    .nav-card {
      background: var(--panel);
      border: 2px solid var(--border);
      padding: 20px;
      transition: all 0.3s;
      cursor: pointer;
      text-decoration: none;
      display: block;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 255, 0, 0.2);
    }

    .nav-card:hover {
      background: rgba(0, 255, 0, 0.1);
      box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 255, 0, 0.5);
      transform: translateY(-5px);
    }

    .nav-card h2 {
      color: var(--fg);
      font-size: 18px;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .nav-card p {
      color: #888;
      font-size: 11px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .info-section {
      background: var(--panel);
      border: 2px solid var(--border);
      padding: 20px;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }

    .info-section h3 {
      color: var(--accent);
      font-size: 14px;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }

    .info-section ul {
      list-style: none;
      padding-left: 20px;
    }

    .info-section li {
      color: var(--fg);
      font-size: 11px;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .info-section li:before {
      content: "▸ ";
      color: var(--accent);
      margin-right: 5px;
    }

    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 40px;
      padding: 20px;
      color: #666;
      font-size: 10px;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
    }

    a {
      color: var(--fg);
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    a:hover {
      color: var(--accent);
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>◉ PROJECT DASHBOARD ◉</h1>

    <div class="nav-grid">
      <a href="?page=MD" class="nav-card">
        <h2>▸ MAP VISUALIZATION</h2>
        <p>Interactive zip code network map showing connections from target location to all respondent locations. Features automatic route tracing along roads.</p>
      </a>

      <a href="?page=dashboard" class="nav-card">
        <h2>▸ DATA DASHBOARD</h2>
        <p>View analytics, charts, and statistics from your collected data. Real-time updates and export capabilities.</p>
      </a>

      <a href="?page=reports" class="nav-card">
        <h2>▸ REPORTS</h2>
        <p>Generate comprehensive reports, export data in various formats, and schedule automated reports.</p>
      </a>

      <a href="?page=settings" class="nav-card">
        <h2>▸ SETTINGS</h2>
        <p>Configure application settings, manage data sources, and customize visualizations.</p>
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="info-section">
      <h3>▸ Quick Links</h3>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="?page=MD">Open Map Visualization</a> - View network connections</li>
        <li><a href="#" onclick="refreshData()">Refresh Data</a> - Pull latest from spreadsheet</li>
        <li><a href="#" onclick="viewSheet()">View Source Sheet</a> - Open FRC sheet</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="info-section">
      <h3>▸ System Information</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Data Source: Sheet "FRC", Column F (Current 5 Digit Zip Code)</li>
        <li>Target Location: 5317 Charlotte St, Kansas City, MO 64110</li>
        <li>Auto-Routing: Enabled (starts automatically on map page)</li>
        <li>Last Updated: <span id="lastUpdate">Loading...</span></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      POWERED BY GOOGLE APPS SCRIPT // <?= new Date().getFullYear() ?>
    </div>
  </div>

